        weighing
        1
        Weighed stoichiometrically to carbonized ampoule. Barium added last to avoid contact with ampoule during reaction

        Sealed
        1
        Evacuated ampoule and sealed with H2/O2 torch

        annealing
        1
        Ba lumps reacted but not homogeneous. Small Ba reaction with silica
